author: Anonymous Scale
title: Setting up again
question: Hi, do I need to go through the setup steps again if I'm retaking the course this term? I haven't uninstalled DrRacket or done anything else to it so I was just wondering if I'd need to set up again for a different term or something.
instructor_answer:
You should be fine if everything was working well for you at the end of last term.
You may need to do the CS run-getacct step though.  Download the test file and try handing it in to be sure.
